nl.tudelft.simulation.dsol.formalisms.devs.ESDEVS

Class AtomicModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.tudelft.simulation.event.EventProducer
      • nl.tudelft.simulation.dsol.formalisms.devs.ESDEVS.AbstractDEVSModel

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, nl.tudelft.simulation.event.EventProducerInterface

    public abstract class AtomicModel
extends AbstractDEVSPortModel
    AtomicModel class. Implements the Classic Parallel DEVS Atomic Model with Ports cf Zeigler et al (2000), section 4.2.2. and section 4.3 (pp. 84 ff). The algorithms for parallel DEVS are explained in Chapters 6 and 7.
